{"about_the_game":"Vertigo 2 is a single-player adventure built from the ground up for VR.<br><br>Deep underground in the reaches of Quantum Reactor VII, you awake to finish your journey home. You\u2019ll have to face bizarre alien flora and fauna leaking from other universes - and deadly android security forces whose job is to purge the reactor of all life. Try to determine who to trust as sinister agents lurk just out of sight.<br><br>Key features include:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Huge, bespoke world design \u2013 an incredible range of environments makes Vertigo 2 much more of an adventure than Vertigo 1.<br></li><li>Enemy variety \u2013 dozens of creatures and robots are waiting to be discovered.<br></li><li>Hybrid locomotion \u2013 both smooth locomotion and teleportation are viable.<br></li><li>State of the art VR weapons \u2013 carry an arsenal of 14 weapons, all with unique reload mechanics.<br></li><li>Fully voiced characters \u2013 a diverse cast brings the many characters of Vertigo 2 to life.<br></li><li>Original soundtrack \u2013 hours of original songs and scoring.<br></li><li>Intense boss fights \u2013 Vertigo is notorious for its ambitious boss encounters, and Vertigo 2 brings 10 brand new bosses.<br></li><li>Substantial campaign \u2013 18 chapters long, Vertigo 2\u2019s story has many times as much content as Vertigo 1.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Armed and Dangerous","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/843390/e6ce8b904e57c54d0ff5a222fe91bd9446617093.jpg"},{"name":"Tailgunner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/843390/b18d651120de1a26e5e72ddfb975f0c32fa75e55.jpg"},{"name":"Thermal Entropy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/843390/073e3da3e0ba1e3709f323dd3d5f118009acf62a.jpg"},{"name":"The Hunt","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/843390/bdfc57195bd157cc43dd